title: Mirrors Edge: Catalyst + 2DLC

Mirror's Edge: Catalyst v1.0.3.47248 + 2 DLC

Release Date: June 7, 2016
Genres/Tags: Arcade, Platform adventure, Open world, First-person, 3D
Developer: DICE
Publisher: Electronic Arts
Platform: PC [Repack]
Engine: Frostbite 3

Interface Language: Russian, French, Portuguese, Chinese, Italian, English, German, Polish, Spanish
Audio Language: Russian, French, Italian, English, German, Spanish
Crack: built-in (CPY)

Minimum requirements:
Operating System: Windows 7 / Windows 8 / Windows 10 (64-bits only)
Processor: Intel i3-3250 / AMD FX6350
RAM: 6 GB
Video Card: NVIDIA GeForce GTX 650 Ti (2GB) / AMD Radeon R9 270x (2GB)
DirectX: 11
HDD Space: 24 GB (~31 GB during installation)

Description:

Mirror's Edge Catalyst is a first-person action-adventure game in which the player takes control of Faith Connors as she progresses through a futuristic city named Glass. Similar to the original Mirror's Edge, players traverse the city using aspects of urban exploration and parkour movements to complete missions and evade or fight enemies.
